Tetress AI Game Agent
An intelligent AI agent for Tetress – a two-player strategy game on an 11×11 toroidal board (like a donut-shaped Tetris battlefield). Players take turns placing tetrominoes until one can’t move or the board fills up.
What it does
It plays as either Red or Blue and always chooses the smartest tetromino placement. Using minimax search with alpha-beta pruning and lookahead (depth 3), it anticipates the opponent’s moves and picks placements that block them as much as possible while keeping strong board control.
